      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i was looking at my mortgage statement from wells fargo and im kinda confused. i have a 30 year fixed at 6.5%. i basically want to know why in the first few years almost none of my monthly payment actually goes toward the house. like if i look at year 5 vs year 25, how much of my payment is going to interest vs principal? can u explain how that works?",
